# React Application Only

This project has two codebases:
- **`iris-react/`** — the active React/Vite/Tailwind dashboard (THIS is the live web app)
- **Root-level Python files** (`app.py`, `components/`, etc.) — legacy Streamlit app, NOT actively used

## Rules

- ALL new features, pages, and components MUST be built in `iris-react/`
- NEVER build features in the Streamlit app unless explicitly asked
- Use the existing React patterns: React Router for pages, Zustand for state, Recharts for charts, Tailwind CSS for styling, Framer Motion for animations
- New pages go in `iris-react/src/views/`, routes in `App.tsx`, nav items in `src/lib/constants.ts`, icons in `src/components/layout/Navigation.tsx`
- Use `GlassCard` for containers, `motion` for animations, `cn()` for class merging
- Use `formatCurrency()`, `formatNumber()`, `formatPercent()` from `src/lib/utils.ts`
- The dev server runs via `npm run dev` in `iris-react/`
